4. FlashAttention (Tri Dao)
---------------------------

PMetal implements the FlashAttention-2 algorithm for Metal, based on the
algorithm described in the original paper. The basic fused cross-entropy
kernel also follows the online softmax approach from the Flash-Attention
Triton implementation. Both are independent Metal reimplementations; no
source code was used from the original implementation.

