5. Unsloth (Unsloth AI, Inc.)
------------------------------

PMetal's fused linear cross-entropy and fused LoRA kernels are independent
Metal implementations informed by algorithmic techniques from the Unsloth
project. The chunked vocabulary cross-entropy approach and fused LoRA
forward/backward strategy follow designs described in Unsloth's source.
No source code was copied from the original repository.

